---
title: Duck a L'Orange with Garlic Greens & Duck-Fat Potatoes
description: Spoil yourself tonight with classic French-style cooking at its finest. The rich orange and apricot sauce glazes the duck breast
for a punch of sweet and savoury flavours that work stunningly. Complemented by crispy duck fat potatoes and tender baby
broccoli, it’s time to whack on your fancy pajamas and settle in for a gourmet delight.
